被淹没在酒吧后面，试图接受他们甚至在那里，然后小费就在上面。我终于有机会停下来打扫卫生，多和他说话并感谢他。我知道我一边哭一边感谢他，但他不知道这对我到底意味着什么。” </p><figure id="attachment_3814221" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814221" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814221" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/post-malone@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814221" class="wp-caption-text">波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 在 2024 年博纳罗 (Bonnaroo) 表演。图片来源：Erika Goldring/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>四月，波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>一起成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">科切拉 (Coachella) 音乐节两个周末的主角</a>。在科切拉音乐节结束后，波斯蒂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-announces-2025-us-the-big-ass-stadium-tour-with-jelly-roll-and-more-3814178">将于四月底至七月初开始北美体育场巡演</a>。</p><p>在体育场演出期间，嘉宾<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jelly-roll">Jelly Roll</a>和创作型歌手塞拉·费雷尔 (Sierra Ferrell) 将与他一起参加。波斯特·马龙体育场之旅的门票现已发售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fpost-malone-tickets%2Fartist%2F2119390">在这里</a>购买。</p><p> Post Malone 的最新专辑《F-1 Trillion》于 8 月推出，这是他于 2023 年发行的第五张录音室专